        WHEN segment = 'SME' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS SME,
    CASE 
        WHEN segment = 'LAM' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS LAM,
    CASE 
        WHEN segment = 'KAM' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS KAM
FROM (
    SELECT 
        yearmonth.column_2 * 100 / SUM(yearmonth.column_2) OVER (PARTITION BY transactions_1k.column_3 ORDER BY transactions_1k.column_1) - 
        yearmonth.column_2 * 100 / SUM(yearmonth.column_2) OVER (PARTITION BY transactions_1k.column_3 ORDER BY transactions_1k.column_1) AS percentage_change,
        segment
    FROM (
        SELECT 
            column_8, 
            CASE 
                WHEN column_7 = 0 THEN 'EUR' ELSE 'USD' END AS currency,
            CASE 
                WHEN column_2 = 2012 THEN 'SME'
                WHEN column_2 = 2013 THEN 'LAM'
                ELSE 'KAM'
            END AS segment
        FROM transactions_1k
    ) AS subquery
) AS subquery2;
